# Exclude everything by default, then include only what this build needs.
# Docker BuildKit picks up this file automatically when the dockerfile path is
# attestation-attester/tpm-platform-attest/Dockerfile and the build context is
# the repository root. OpenSSL, gencmpclient and libattest are all cloned from
# their pinned branches inside the Dockerfile, so none of them comes from this
# context — only the scripts below do.

**

# ── Attester scripts ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
!attestation-attester/
!attestation-attester/tpm-platform-attest/
!attestation-attester/tpm-platform-attest/entrypoint.sh
!attestation-attester/tpm-platform-attest/provision.sh
